Comment: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:29.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Don't wanna die before we see our fire inside, so
Comment: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(We can fight!)
Comment: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:34.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}泥まみれのその表情が見据えてる先へ
Comment: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(We can fly!)
Comment: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:40.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}流れ落ちる汗が全て無駄に終わるとしても
Comment: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}戦うことだけは忘れはしないだろう
Comment: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつでも笑える強い君の
Comment: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}泣き顔は誰も知らないから
Comment: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:55.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}心のアザは消えないけど
Comment: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(Let's go!)
Comment: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}(Get up, get up, get up!)
Comment: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}You always never gave up,
Comment: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}You never gave up
Comment: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そう nothing's too late
Comment: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうやってnever wake up,
Comment: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}You never wake up
Comment: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}夢見て行こうぜ
Comment: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:10.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつか嘆いてた笑えない世界は
Comment: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}どこまでも笑って
Comment: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:14.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうさ
Comment: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Get up, get up, get up!
Comment: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}駆け抜ければいい
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Comment: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:34.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}季節が　駆けてく　息を　きらして
Comment: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:41.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}必死に　ついてく　淡すぎる衝動
Comment: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:48.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}気づけば　誰もが　顔を　変えてく
Comment: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}周りを　気にして　白を黒という
Comment: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:01.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}自分にウソはつきたくない
Comment: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:08.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}幸せの　形は　ひとつだけじゃないから
Comment: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:15.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}変わる強さより　変わらない強さ
Comment: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:22.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}心に手をあてて　自分自身を今　愛してあげよう
Comment: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:29.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}変わる強さより　変わらない強さ
Comment: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:36.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}誰かのためじゃなく　今、未来へと
